snippet.title: Tunche – Kickstarter Trailer (Steam, Xbox One, Playstation 4, Switch)
snippet.description:
Tunche is a charming, hand-drawn 2D Beat ‘em up - mixed with roguelike elements, local co-op and a dash of shaman witchcraft. Now on Kickstarter ► https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/750271334/tunche

Tunche is coming to Kickstarter on January 14th! 

To keep up with the latest news and updates, follow Tunche's pages on: 
Discord ► https://discord.gg/VsHxMJw 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/tunchegame 
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/playtunche

Music - http://2mello.net/
